     <profileDesc>
        <abstract><p>In recognition of his loyalty and efforts towards cultivating and populating the area, the landlord (chaudhri) <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>  of district (pargana) <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName> received a grant of 11 villages and 3,750 bighas in land, including orchards of mango and other trees. He is enjoined to remain loyal to the government and to regularly set aside money for the villages' expenses.</p></abstract>       
        
