  <text>
      <body>
         
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1675_dai_lns235ms_x_r.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre"><p>هو</p></div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1"><p>He [God] is</p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="top right"><p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
            <persName ref="#islamKhan">اسلام خان</persName>
            بن حسین علی مرید
            <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">عالمگیر</persName>
            بادشاه
            <unclear><date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>۱۰۸۰</num></date></unclear>
            </mentioned></stamp>
         </p></div> 
         <div corresp="#orig_div2"  xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#islamKhan">Islam Khan</persName>, son of Hussein Ali, disciple of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_badshah">Badshah</ref> <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Alamgir</persName> <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1080</date></mentioned></stamp></p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>متصدیان مهمات حال و استقبال پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               سرکار
               <placeName ref="#mandu">مندو</placeName>
               بدانند که چون بعرض رسید
               <lb/>که 
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتمداس</persName> 
               چودری پرگنه مذکور در دولتخواهی و آبادانکاری سعی
               <app>
                  <rdg cert="medium">کاملی</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="low">کامیابی</rdg>
               </app>
               بجا می آرد
               <lb/>موضع
               <placeName ref="#ahu">آهو</placeName>
               وغیره یازده موضع
               <measure type="land" unit="bigha" quantity="3750">سه هزار هفت صد و پنجاه
                  <g ref="#siyaq">۳۷۵۰</g>
                  بیگهه</measure>  
               زمین و اشجار امبه حسب الضمن
               <lb/>بموجب نشان والا و اسناد جاگیرداران و حکام سابق در وجه انعام و نانکار
               <lb/>خود با فرزندان مقرر دارد لهذا مواضع و اراضی و اشجار را بدستور سابق
               <lb/>بحالداشته شد می باید که تصرف مومی الیه  واگذارند که حاصلات آنرا
               <lb/>سال بسال و فصل بفصل صرف مایحتاج خودها نموده مراسم دولتخواهی و آبادانکاری
               <lb/>چنان بتقدیم رساند که آبادانی و معموری پرگنه روز افزون گردد در اینباب
               <lb/>تاکید تمام دانسته حسب المسطور بعمل آرند هر ساله سند مجدد نطلبند تحریر فی تاریخ غره رمضان سنه
               <date><num>۱۰۸۳</num></date>
               عملی
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">  
            <p>
               <lb/>The important officials of the present and future of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">sarkar</ref> <placeName ref="#mandu">Mandu</placeName>, know that since it has been petitioned 
               <lb/>that <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of the said <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>, is making perfect efforts towards the well-being of the government and in cultivating and populating [the area], 
               <lb/>the village of <placeName ref="#ahu">Ahu</placeName>, etc. [in total] eleven<note>The unusually tight spacing of the prefix changing this word from ten to eleven suggests it was added later. On the verso only ten villages are mentioned.</note> villages and <measure type="land" unit="bigha" quantity="3750">three thousand and seven hundred and fifty<note>The unusually tight word spacing and odd and extra dot placement suggest this total amount was altered from five hundred and fifty. In the particulars on the verso in one place only five hundred and fifty bighas of land are mentioned.</note> <g ref="#siyaq">3750</g><note>This amount is written in <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_siyaq">siyaq</ref> above the line.</note> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_bigha">bighas</ref></measure> of land and mango trees, according to the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_zimn">zimn</ref>, 
               <lb/>on the basis of the exalted <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nishan">nishan</ref> and documents of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jagirdar">jagirdars</ref> and the previous governors, is allocated in <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_inam">inʿam</ref> and <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nankar">nankar</ref> 
               <lb/>to him [<persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>] together with his children. Therefore the villages and lands and trees, according to former practice, 
               <lb/>are set aside. It is necessary that [these lands] are placed in the possession of the said person such that the income [from these lands] 
               <lb/>year by year and season by season are appointed for their necessary expenses, [and that] they prioritize the duties respecting loyalty [toward the government] and cultivation [of the area] 
               <lb/>such that the habitation and cultivation and governance of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> grows every day. In this matter, 
               <lb/>knowing all to be settled, they should execute [it] as written [and] they should not demand a fresh <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sanad">sanad</ref> every year. Written on the 1st of Ramzan in the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_amali">ʿamali</ref> year <date>1083</date>. Ended. 
            </p> 
         </div>
         
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1675_dai_lns235ms_x_v.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right"><p><unclear>قلمنماید</unclear></p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4"><p><unclear>Written</unclear></p></div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top left">   
            <p>پروانه نواب
               <persName ref="#islamKhan">اسلام خان</persName>
            </p></div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5"><p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nawab">Nawab</ref> <persName ref="#islamKhan">Islam Khan</persName></p></div>
        
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               ضمن نویسی
            </p></div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div6" xml:id="trans_div6">
            <p>
               Writing of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_zimn">zimn</ref>
            </p></div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div7" xml:lang="per" type="particulars" rend="middle centre"><p>
               <lb/><unclear>مقرر</unclear>
               ضمن از آنچه که بموجب
               <unclear>ند عامله</unclear>
